# Email Nodes Module

This directory contains the email processing nodes implementation for the Office Automation Platform.

## Structure

- `types.ts` - Core types and interfaces
- `parser.ts` - Email parser (mailparser wrapper)
- `filter.ts` - Email filter engine
- `template.ts` - Template engine (Handlebars wrapper)
- `adapters/` - Provider adapters (IMAP, Gmail, Outlook)
- `utils/` - Utility functions (encryption, etc.)
